Officers of the Lagos State Rapid Response Squad (RRS) have paraded two suspected traffic robbers in separate incidents between Magodo Estate and Otedola bridge, Lagos State. Korede Saheed, 29, was arrested on Thursday, May 26, 2022 night, while the other suspect, Yahaya Faisal, 22, was arrested on Friday night, May 27, 2022.
   
According to Lagos State Police Public Relations Officer (PPRO), Benjamin Hundeyin, luck ran out on the suspects when their victims quickly reached out to RRS officers on patrol in the area. 